snippet.title: Best VGM 1009 - Ms. Pac-Man Maze Madness - Haunted Halloween
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

PS1 / N64 / Dreamcast
Ms. Pac-Man Maze Madness (2000)
Haunted Halloween
Jon Holland
